          {
            "text": "Here are some options for acne facial treatments in Katy, Texas:\n\n*   **AcneFix:** They offer personalized acne treatments combining expert care with proven methods. Their services include acne consultation, acne consultation and treatment, and acne treatment sessions with extractions, high-frequency treatment, and LED light therapy. They focus on identifying your acne type, skin tolerance, and triggers to create a customized plan.\n*   **Luminous MediSpa:** They offer specialized acne facials designed to combat acne, improve skin health, and boost confidence. Their acne facials include a comprehensive evaluation, deep cleansing, exfoliation, extractions, acne-fighting products, and hydration.\n*   **Spavia Cinco Ranch:** They offer a purifying acne facial rich in Mangosteen extract, providing antioxidant, antibacterial, and anti-inflammatory actions. The facial helps heal and reduce blackheads and blemishes. It includes extractions, a blend of white and green clays, and a relaxing massage.\n*   **Face to Face Spa:** This med spa offers facials designed to address a range of concerns, including acne reduction. Options include classic facials and Hydrafacials, with more specialized treatments like chemical peels, microneedling, microdermabrasion, and dermaplaning. New clients can enjoy a 60-minute premium medi-facial with a choice of chemical peel or microdermabrasion at a discounted rate.\n*   **Le Chloé Med Spa:** They offer various facial treatments, and their aesthetic experts can recommend a facial that is perfect for your skin concerns and type. They offer an Acne Light Facial, chemical peels, microdermabrasion, and microneedling.\n*   **Hibiscus Aesthetics & Wellness:** They offer personalized acne and acne scar treatments, including AviClear™ Laser Treatment, chemical peels, and microneedling. They also offer NEOCLEAR BY AEROLASE® ACNE TREATMENT, which targets excess sebum production, inflammation, and the p. acnes bacteria.\n*   **Massage Envy - Katy:** They offer results-driven facials and skin care services designed to focus on your specific goals. They offer a Clarifying Acne Chemical Exfoliation. More advanced treatments such as Microderm Infusion, Chemical Peel/Exfoliation, and Dermaplaning are also available.\n"
          }
        ],
